In order to run these tests in tap do from local machine or CI portal:
 1) activate the tap environment:
    source tap/bin/activate
 2) tap run edr_plugin.component --debug-loop                           #run the pytests and robot tests
 3) tap run edr_plugin.component.ubuntu1804_x64_pytest --debug-loop     #runs the pytests only
 4) tap run edr_plugin.component.ubuntu1804_x64_robot --debug-loop      #runs the robot tests only
 5) tap run edr_plugin.coverage --debug-loop                   #runs both pytests and robot for bullseye coverage, the branch must have a coverage build, master or ends with 'coverage'

For information on running outside TAP see PytestScripts/README